comment: /**  * All of the named writeables needed to deserialize the instances of  * {@linkplain BucketExtractor}s.  */
code: /**  * All of the named writeables needed to deserialize the instances of  * {@linkplain BucketExtractor}s.  */ public static List<NamedWriteableRegistry.Entry> getNamedWriteables() {     List<NamedWriteableRegistry.Entry> entries = new ArrayList<>().     entries.add(new Entry(BucketExtractor.class, CompositeKeyExtractor.NAME, CompositeKeyExtractor::new)).     entries.add(new Entry(BucketExtractor.class, ComputingExtractor.NAME, ComputingExtractor::new)).     entries.add(new Entry(BucketExtractor.class, MetricAggExtractor.NAME, MetricAggExtractor::new)).     entries.add(new Entry(BucketExtractor.class, TopHitsAggExtractor.NAME, TopHitsAggExtractor::new)).     entries.add(new Entry(BucketExtractor.class, ConstantExtractor.NAME, ConstantExtractor::new)).     return entries. }
